items.text: Ask for a bib if you're eating crab.
Краб с чесноком и луком!)
Chilli crabs and black pepper crabs! Go early to sit near the sea.
Steamed prawns and white rice. Plain simple heaven.

Overrated. You can get bigger crabs at other joints with better prices. Have a shot at the bamboo clams with minced garlic. Delicious! The crispy baby squids are not to be missed as well.
Chillicrab
싱가폴 오면 한번쯤 가볼만한 칠리/페퍼크랩 음식점. 개인적으론 페퍼크랩이 더 맛있음
I don't like too much sauce on my crab. So chilli crab not for me. I chose the butter crab.  Very good!
With Apple lim and @ivanchan90
Try the crap
Very nice and fresh seafood served here with nice seaview!! Worth the try!
Délicieux fruits de mer tres frais dans ce restaurant en bord de mer, dont le Chili crab. Avec une bouteille de vin + crevettes aux céréales + légumes = 100€ pour 2. Pas donné mais ça vaut le détour
Pepper crab,chilli crab,sambal kangkong, roasted chicken & sweet & sour fish.. can never go wrong!
Chili Crab, black pepper crab, seafood fried rice.
Horrible service during weekend
Bad service. Waited long for our food
Always come back for the chili crab. The service was horrible compare to higher-scale restaurant, but that's the Singaporean standard anyway. Don't care too much lah just get your delicious food.
Didn't enjoyed the crab, you tiao and mee goreng earlier. Maybe its their "off" day today!
Get the chili crab and the black pepper crab, sit outside with a beer.
Try the Chilled Mango with Roasted Duck Salad! Tangy, sweet with a touch of spice
Skip Jumbo, go to Longhouse. Better crab, better cereal prawns. And coffee pork ribs!
Expensive. Not nice. Not worth the long wait. My first and last time at jumbo. Seriously, the crab CANNOT make it
Simply love their service here..
칠리크랩은 요리하는데 45분 걸립니다. 헐...
The austere chilli crab for tea. #jumboappetite
Seafood is no longer as good as before.
Avoid drunken prawns, broth lousy, prawns not fresh.
Chilli crabs and cereal prawns is a must try
Order: 1. Black pepper crab 2. Drunken prawns 3. Steamed Garupa fish 4. Dou Miau greens 4. Baby Cailan 5. Fried rice with seafood
Best place to get crab! Chilli grab is more popular but they also offer black pepper crab and salty egg crab. Yum!
I've always loved jumbo since I was a child :3
What else? Of course Chili Crab!!
Go early to avoid the queue and dont get too hang up on svc though they are really not bad - u cant go wrong with their black pepper or chilli crabs - getting expensive though
Шикарный краб ( чеснок и лук), сашими из лобстера на отлично!!!!

Spicy Singaporian crabs...
Perfect chilli crab:) beautifully view, but always pretty full:)
Amazing chilli crab. Try sit outside if it's not raining. You can also buy the chilli crab paste..
the cereal prawns are to die for! :)
Server taking order has real good customer service! 👍🏼👍🏼 providing us with additional Chilli crab sauce as when the mantou is served, the sauce is already all gone
The chilli crab isn't as gd as what it potrays it to be. But d black pepper crab is a must-have! Other than that I think it's overrated. Too ex & can gt much better food elsewhere at cheaper price.
The Chilli crab is too sweet. I will call it sweet crab. Pepper crab is better
等了好久都还没上菜，都1小时了，怎么那么慢？！
chili crab and salted egg prawn. yumyumyum. super yum
Just get the crabs and some veg, rest of the menu hugely disappointing. In fact it is down right terrible fare and will only take away from the sublime crabs (chilli and black pepper).
Abysmal service and food is average at best. Very sad for me personally cos they used to be excellent when I was growing up. Always looked forward to coming here for seafood. I'll look elsewhere now.
Chilli crabs have a great taste, must have eat.... need bring credit card or much cash ;) it's premium price.... overall 9/10
ガーリック蟹はめちゃめちゃ辛いから、辛いの苦手な人は要注意。
Great sea view if you go early.
The service is bad here, I cancelled my 1hour long order and left early. Dont come!
Rectangle table for 4 is only enough for 2
Food takes super long to come esp when there are tour groups arriving for dinner
Pretty good chilly crab and black pepper crab!
Bamboo clams r very tasty though pricy..
Garlic and black peppers crabs are both amazing!
Nice seafood but gotta wait for 30mins even though we've booked a table. Price is a bit high for the food they serve but it's tasty. Didn't like the crowd at all as it's way too packed.
I Love Seafood
The blackpepper crab is so damn good!
Second time here with relatives, second time they bungle up orders and make customers wait until they walk off pissed :(
The scallops and asparagus with garlic and oyster sauce is very nice. Order fried buns to soak the chilli crab gravy. Oh, and ask to sit outdoors looking out to the sea, ships and planes flying in.
chilli crab tasted flat.
The big name and the delicious seafood in Singapore
Yummy chilli crabs..finish off the gravy with fried buns..
Good crab and seafood. Make sure you book as it gets very full.
Chilli crab was disappointing
Overrated! The services were so bad.
Eat the JUMBO Chilli Crab while watching the ships. If you don't mess, you didn't do it right.
chili crab with fried mantou. salted egg prawn.heaven!!
disappointed that dishes were served looking less than appealing and food was below lukewarm.
The view is good, the food is even better, weekdays is less crowded and speed of serving is really fast
The chill crab very nice and big and butter crab also . The butter crab sauce nice too .
Foods wasn't as delicious as before. Service could improve a bit more.
Love the black pepper crabs here
The crab is very good, stick to the crab though as the other dishes are very average.
Sitting close to the sea. The chilli crab is a must do.
Slurps ah
Unfriendly and rude waitresses here. Poor service. Didn't enjoy dinner here.
Trust me: You get adequate customer service only when you're a Caucasian, or look like a foreigner here.
Great chilli crabs :)
Chilli crab tasted better this time round
The Deep Fried Garupa with a spicy base!!
The seafood is ok, but way overpriced. Tourist trap much! Do come here for the ambience though, esp. if u hv an overseas guest.
이것저것 맛볼수 있는게 좋으나 현지인의 안내를 받아야 함

Try the satay here. It's good.
Food is just delish!
Nice crab 😋😋
Chili crab - need I say more. This branch has the best location (by the beach)
Obviously chilli crab is a must. Pepper too. Horribly expensive.
The ladies servers have a really bad attitude. Try being served by a guy, his service was exceptionally good. Food was generally acceptable.
The chilli crabs aren't too bad. (And I generally never like Singapore Chili Crab sauce)
Great seefod!!! .. A huge restaurant :-)

Get your chilli and pepper crab fix here at the original Jumbo. Don't forget an order of mantou to sop up that sauce too.
Tasty (but expensive)....try pepper crab as a starter and chilli crab with rice !
Free wifi!!
Order chilli crab and buns. The sweet buns you can eat with the jumbo chilli crab sause
One of the best seafood places in Singapore. Call a day in advance for the jumbo chili crab and bring a change of clothes if you won't wear a bib.
Chilli crab! Great outlook. Very popular
Has whiskey but serves per bottle, not by the glass

first time tried the pepper crab @Jumbo, not nice at all , under seasoned , spicy cod fish is yummy but presentation looks funny, looks like a desert dish, great service and environment !
Nuts and tea are not free!
予約ができないので、早目の来店がおすすめです。料理は最高！
Flower Clams is absolutely a must!!
Food is nice but today's service is terrible and the bill was wrong. Best not to sit too inside upstairs
After sister's wedding we are just go to Jumbo Restaurant to have a dinner w/ Yeo Family and my family Thedpun Im happy and congratulate to my sister ^^
Give us Canadian crab cost more and no good than the normal crab , the staff tried to pull the fast one ....
Шикарный краб, любой из меню этого чудесного ресторана на побережье Сингапура!
Salted Egg Crab is something you have to try other than the boring Chili Crab....
Food here is always delicious.. cant go wrong wiyh the seafood.. efficient service too
The chilli crab is not that fanstatic.. Their standard drop.. So disappointed! The service is quite alright.. (@,@)

9 out of 9 dishes, all very salty...
Clam sashimi, black pepper and salted crabs are winner!
The only place where i'll eat Seafood...awesome..nice ambience n nice food..not forgetting nice drinks too!
Absolutely packed to the brim. Enjoyed the Chilli crab with freshly baked bread rolls. Delicious !
Chili Crab

Cannot get in even if you have advanced reservation. And even then, was assigned to a small table for 5 pax. Bad svc, try other restaurants.
This is the main shop of the famous chain. The food here has more choices like many chinese restaurant, but overall just OK, nothing bad but no memorable dish.

Decent dinner will be Black Pepper Crab, Seafood & Vegetables Soup, Crispy-fried Baby Squid, Fried Rice with Seafood. I also highly recommend Fresh Lime with Aloe Vera. The seaview'll make the rest...
Pepper crabs are spicier than chilli crabs; vegetarians .. This is not the right place to be.
Chilli crabs & black pepper crabs are OISHIIIII! 
